ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f792681e1d53b9ae08faebcba61722f32cd9d163","tid":2086641,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd7af56166684b094e2632cf872276c20f68ec0e","tid":2086641,"uid":338439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"71照出ar dklm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"手足，大家聽日見，準備好道具比國際傳媒影啊<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=7c365117\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國廢架制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4cee0568637e9d04ea2dfaf12f565b5cfde0b18d","tid":2086641,"uid":62749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"未砌好個條文實施咩?<br />\n實施一國一制，國安執法?"},{"pid":"f3afd7f0eea55fdac6b094bcba71c54c1c84aaae","tid":2086641,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x59TBtx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx59TBtx.png&h=e21122db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ab6901ec026aa55d0f52059f4cdc4d10a7a9ce9","tid":2086641,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:01:53.000Z","msg":"推 7.1大遊行 tweet國際戰線 黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"bc35c44f95a2566d9f344cbd4706f1aab0114371","tid":2086641,"uid":60376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"死亡筆記今日生效 遲d諗到先寫野落去"},{"pid":"f558926e8f474a644b0fb87e8dbe8e649af4914b","tid":2086641,"uid":53610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"但係我連內文係乜都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019bc8cf49e4aa6401e6a6b8cdecd23deaff5233","tid":2086641,"uid":11845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"所以條文係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61962e4fba3b16403f268ec6ccb774f4ce2a73c7","tid":2086641,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019bc8cf49e4aa6401e6a6b8cdecd23deaff5233","tid":2086641,"uid":11845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"所以條文係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"唔知！"},{"pid":"432dd4013ffc4a9b7e04c814c96a54104b353ab7","tid":2086641,"uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike